690
00:49:06,450 --> 00:49:08,379
ton pote qui a tué sa femme

691
00:49:08,421 --> 00:49:10,198
éclatait la gueule à Bruce !

692
00:49:10,225 --> 00:49:11,494
Quoi ?

693
00:49:11,744 --> 00:49:12,688
Salut, Randy.

694
00:49:12,714 --> 00:49:13,664
Cliff !

695
00:49:13,761 --> 00:49:15,618
C'est quoi ce bordel, mec ?

696
00:49:15,835 --> 00:49:16,996
Permettez-moi de dire....

697
00:49:17,080 --> 00:49:19,017
